    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      StructureSaveConfiguration createSaveConfiguration()
      Creates a saveConfiguration for the minimal required parameters in order to load and save structures from and to your world folder. The structure will always be identified by the unique key from the combined author, saveName and world.
      boolean load()
      Uses the saveConfiguration to load a structure to the given target location.
      void save()
      Uses the saveConfiguration to store a structure by the source location and given offSet.
      void save()
      Uses the saveConfiguration to store a structure by the source location and between the corner location.
